AFTERBURNER 2
=============
Level Select - When the start prompt appears on the title screen, press and
hold button C - followed by A and then B. Press START. A level select screen
will appear that can transport you almost anywhere in the game.


AIR DIVER
=========
Secret Modes - Start the game and go to an area on the map with no enemies. 
Hold START and Press A, B, C, B, A, A, B, C, B, A, B. Let go of START for
invinciblity, hold A for fight ace, hold B for the mothership and hold C for
the last Boss. Continue to hold as designated while you leave the hanger.
Once the round begins, let go of the buttons.


ALIEN STORM
===========
Stay Alive After You Die - To do this trick, you must have enough energy to
do your special move. First you must be the robot, Scooter. When you die, 
use its special attack move and it will end up with no energy, but it will
not be dead. Do this trick every time you die, and (if you are good enough
to power up your life again) you will not lose any lives.


ALTERED BEAST
=============
Change Characters - To change your alter ego, at the title screen, press the
pad DOWN and LEFT while holding all three buttons and press START. 

Level Select - At the title screen, hold B and press START for a play select
menu and when selecting a round, hold A and press START to choose it. 

Sound Test - At the title screen, press UP and RIGHT while holding A and C 
buttons, and then press START for a sound test.


ARCH RIVALS
===========
Gain Possession of Ball - You can automatically take possession of the ball
at the beginning of the quarter when playing against the computer. Before the
game starts, when you are shown the locker room, hold button A and press
START while still holding it to get into game. When the tip off starts, you
will automatically hit the ball to your other player. To do this trick in
the other quarters, just hold the A button during the commentator's screen
and the halftime show.


ARNOLD PALMER GOLF
==================
Secret Tournament - There is a secret tournament in this game. Enter the
lower case "f" across the top portion of the password box and enter a "9"
across the bottom portion. Do this, and you will be in a new tournament with
a different caddy, who tells you much more than the one in the game.

Hidden Game - To enter the hidden game, hit 100 strokes on any hole. Then,
during the "Game Over" screen, press UP, Up, DOWN, DOWN, LEFT, RIGHT, B, A,
and then START until the game begins.


ARROW FLASH
===========
Invinciblity - At the option mode, change Arrow Flash from Stock to Charge.
Wait for the demo to play (after the story demo) and then hit START until
the game begins. Each time you press C for three to five seconds, you will
become invincible for ten minutes.


BACK TO THE FUTURE 3
====================
Skip Stages - Pause the game at any point and simultanously press these
buttons together in the following order: UP and A, DOWN and A, LEFT and A,
RIGHT and A.


BURNING FORCE
=============
Start With 10 Ships - At the title screen, press B, A, B, A, A, C, A, A.
Then hit START.


BUSTER DOUGLAS BOXING
=====================
Sound Test - To listen to the sounds of the game, press START on controller
2 at the game select screen. Press and hold DOWN on the controller and press
the A button to play the music. Move to the sound effects and after the
first one, press RIGHT for more.


CASTLE OF ILLUSION
==================
Max Out Your Lives - Play the game until you are on level 2-2. Just before
you get to the exit, you will see a Jack-In-The-Box. Kill him, walk to the
left and you will get a bag of power-ups and 1000 points. Now walk back to
the right and stop at the question mark. Go back to the left to get another
1000 points. Mickey gets an extra life every 50,000 points, so repeat this
trick until you have 10 lives.


CENTURIAN: DEFENDER OF ROME
===========================
Passcode - Enter this code on the save game screen to have control of many
ancient countries and one fleet of ships.
                                           BN4Q AUIV W6IQ
                                           ZCA5 555S 73IJ


DECAPATTACK
===========
Airwalk and Life Refill - Here are methods that you can use together. The
first is the airwalk. Press the C button rapidly after you jump. Use the
airwalk to position yourself over one of the red poles found in the game and
then drop straight down onto it. Each time you do this, you will gain a half
of your heart life back and one of the segments on the pole will trun white.

Bypass the Boss - As you approach the last fall before Toady, the second
round Boss, float to the ledge on the left, then jump from ledge to ledge
until you see the sign that says you have cleared the round. Be careful,
though. You must get the special item before you leave the level. If you
fail to do this, you will have to go back to the level and find the item,
plus you will run into the second round Boss!


DESERT STRIKE
=============
Mission Codes - Access the password option by pressing A.

      Campaign #2 - BQJZAEX 
      Campaign #3 - TLJAOAZ
      Campaign #4 - ITOIPEK

Two Extra Lives - To add two lives to your current three, enter TQQLOM on
the password screen. You can then start the game, or put in your own level
code to start on higher levels.

Seven Extra Lives - Start the game with ten lives by entering the code: 
BQQQAEZ.

Attack of Ambassador's Camp in Campaign #3 - 
    1) Get plenty of armor.
    2) Take out the radar - down and to the right of the road approaching
       the camp.
    3) Fly straight up the road towards the camp.
    4) Take out the M-38 with two Hellfires.
    5) Hang a left on the next street and an immediate right around the
       building.
    6) Right around the building will be a tank and a Rapier/SAM gun.
    7) Collect the ambassador - he is under one of the buildings (random).


DEVILISH
========
99 Balls - If you want a stock of 99 balls in your arsenal, go to the title
screen and hold buttons A, C and LEFT on the control pad. When you press
START you will have 99 balls in your possession.


DRAGON'S FURY
=============
99 Balls & 13 million points - Enter the following password: VFELFO78TL
That is the letter O in the password. 


EL VIENTO
=========
Instant Magic - Pause the game during play, and press UP, LEFT, RIGHT, DOWN
and C. You will get one magic each time you do this trick. Repeat it for all
your magic powers.

Clear Scene - At any time during play, pause the game and press UP, LEFT,
RIGHT, DOWN and then B. You will skip the stage you were in and go to the
next one.

Slow Motion - Pause during play and press UP, LEFT, RIGHT, DOWN and then A.
You will be able to move in slow motion with the sound intact.


E-SWAT
======
Level Select - Beat the game and at the ending scene, hold diagonally down
and left on the controller, and all three buttons. Repeatedly push START
until the music comes on. This brings up the music select screen.


F-22
====
Level Codes - To jump ahead to the end of any level, put in these codes:

     For Iraq   - GT8C4A
     For USA    - 6O0A4A
     For Korea  - BH0B8K
     For Russia - KS6A49

Awesome Passcode - Just enter the password: GTGAUO.  Now you must land your
plane, and after you land you will get a surprising screen.


FAIRY TALE ADVENTURE
====================
Play the End Game - To play the end game put in the code:
                    7R2KUL6RSZXSK6NHGSDCB720663R12HO785P


FANTASIA
========
Max Out Your Lives and Magic - First, fight your way to the second stage to
the point where there are platforms that go up. Once there, you must jump up
the platforms to the top where you will get a 1-Up. Next, fight your way
through the level until you get to the point where you are right before the
magic book. Take the magic book and keep moving right until you see a
treasure chest. Go to the chest and you will come out past the paltforms. Go
left and jump back up the platforms. Do this trick as many times as you want.


FERRARI GRAN PRIX CHALLENGE
===========================
Race Select - To choose any race on the circuit, enter the following codes:

  Brazilian GP     San Marino GP    Monaco GP       Canadian GP
  ------------     -------------    ---------       -----------
  55PJ1:ZCPSF      GKBWQ:GF63T      N6MRL:VDDZ1     QHS61:SBQ35
  FTNH2:Z1T6S      PZMGW:CBGTM      FGRFH:4Q41Z     XSVDH:4Q41Z
  L363J:WGFGG      NQ6KS:2CFJT      KLX6W:QKFMP     KQZJS:QKFQR

  French GP        British GP       German GP       Hungarian GP
  ---------        ---------        ---------       ------------
  GVGGP:3JZSR      JHFGV:DJRZB      34XZ6:BG3KC     DLQC3:QFZ3P
  4M4B6:21TNL      VZBBK:J3Z6L      ZWCRC:WWQVV     LDHQ6:21TNL
  NXLP6:G3DJS      MHDNX:G5CCK      LSGZK:S4DMH     NBL1J:B6DQG


FIGHTING MASTERS
================
Warrior vs Same Warrior - Select the two player option at the title screen.
Once you get into the character selection screen, move the cursor to the
warrior that you want to use for this trick. Mow, TIMING IS VERY IMPORTANT.
Have player 1 press DOWN and B at the same time. If your timing was right,
then the name of the warrior under your player's name will be darkened, as
if he/she were chosen. However, your warrior's picture should still remain
in the player 1 icon box. Because the name beneath yours was darkened, your
character still remains available for player 2 to choose. Have player 2
select the same warrior. You will now be fighting warrior vs. warrior.


FLASHBACK
=========
Level Codes:
              1: FALCON      5: BIJOU
              2: DATA        6: BUBBLE
              3: MILORD      7: CLIP
              4: QUICKY


FORGOTTEN WORLDS
================
Unlimited Life - Press START to pause when your life is low, and switch to
controller 2. Press START on controller two for a new life.


GAIRES
======
Invinciblity - Pause, hold buttons A and C, press LEFT and unpause the game.

If that doesn't work try the following: Enter the game configuration mode.
Go to the sound test and select #18. Hold down button A on controller 2.
While doing this, exit the configuration mode on controller #1. Hit Start
once you see the title screen, and you're ready. Now pause the game. Press
and hold down A, C, and Left. At the same time, hit Start. You should now
be invincible.


GHOULS & GHOSTS
===============
Invinciblity Trick - Reset the game four times; press the A button four
times, press UP, DOWN, LEFT and RIGHT on the pad, hold the B button and press
START; hold the C button and press START.

Alternate Invinciblity Trick - Press UP and A, Down and A, LEFT and A, RIGHT
and A. You should hear a short "Harp" sound. When you hear this, hold the B
button and press START. Then, hold C and pres START.


GOLDEN AXE
==========
Level Select - At the character select screen, press button B and hold the
pad DOWN, LEFT and press START simultaneously on ccontroller 1. A small
number will appear in the upper left hand corner of the screen. Move the
number with the pad to change your starting level. 


GOLDEN AXE 2
============
Over 200 Magic Units - Press and hold the A button when fighting the Boss
on any stage. Do not let go of the button until you defeat the Boss and
enter the bonus stage. Release the A button, but do not hit any of the 
wizards or take any magic books. Wait until the next stage and you will be
able to use magic spells whenever you want.

Round Select - When the game starts, hold down the A, B, and C buttons and
press START. Release the B and C buttons, but hold A. Go to the options
screen and press B and C to enter it. Without releasing A, move the cursor
to Exit and press B with C again. While holding the A button, press B and C
together to make your choice of one or two players and press it again to
choose a normal game. Select your character and without releasing the A
button, hold UP on the pad, and press B, C and START simultanously. Select
your round with A and B.

Credit Increase - Get to the title screen and move to "Options." Press
A, B and C simultanously and hold them to enter the options screen. Let go
of A, but keep B and C pressed, Move down to "Exit" and press START. Choose
a 1 or 2 player game by pressing START and then choose a normal game by
pressing the A button. You will then see your credits on the lower right hand
side increased from 3 to 8.

HERZOG ZWEI
===========
Level Codes - There are two different endings. Try the Blue side codes:

   A's: LHGFHCHHKBMH     B's: LHJKHCHKBLP
   C's: LHJKINHKBLD      D's: LJJOIGBAPLG

IMMORTAL, THE
=============
Passcodes:   Level 2:  cddff10006f70    Level 6:  563ff53010a41
             Level 3:  f47ef21000e10    Level 7:  c250f63010a41
             Level 4:  8fdfe31001eb0    Level 8:  e011f730178c1
             Level 5:  94bfb43000eb0


INSPECTOR X
===========
Unlimited Continues - After you see Game Over on the screen, at the continue
mode, push and hold diagonally LEFT and UP. Then press the C button. Each
time you press the C button, your continues increase by one.


JOHN MADDEN FOOTBALL
====================
Stop Opponent's Extra Points - In order to force your opponent to miss his
extra points, keep going off the sides until the ball is on the goal line.
Then when your opponent kicks the ball, it will be too low and he will miss.


JOHN MADDEN FOOTBALL '92
========================
Final Game Code - To play as Chicago against Buffalo, enter B3FM8FB5.

Trick After Touchdown - When you score a touchdown, hold UP and your player
does a back flip. Hold DOWN and he does the Egyptian Dance. Hold LEFT to do
a hand spring and RIGHT to get him to throw up his hands and dance.


KID CHAMELEON
=============
Fight the Last Boss - To get to the final Boss without fighting your way
through every level, try this method. Go to Blue Lake Woods 2 and make your
way through the level, but do not touch the flag to end the level. Get up
on the very last prize block in the level, and push DOWN and RIGHT with the
Jump and Special buttons held. You will be warped to the last Boss.

No Prize Bonus - There is an easy way to earn an extra 5000 points. Just go
through the level, but do not pick up any items. You will receive a 5000
point "No Prize Bonus" when you enter the level.


KRUSTY'S SUPER FUNHOUSE
=======================
Passwords - At the title screen, enter the following level passwords:

    Level 2: WHOAMAMA   Level 3: FLANDERS   
    Level 4: BROCKMAN   Level 5: SIDESHOW


LAKERS VS. CELTICS
==================
Play in World Championship Match - Going into the championships, you will be
the Bulls with a 9-0 record. To play against the Phoenix Suns, enter 296ROS.


LIGHTNING FORCE (Thunder Force 4)
=================================
99 Lives - Wait for the introduction to pass. When the screen says press
START, you should press button A and START together to pull up the 
Configuration screen. Now highlight the number of ships and set the number
to zero. Then Start the game and you will have 99 lives.


MARVEL LAND
===========
Stage Select - When in the Normal Mode, simply enter the password screen and
use the code ARDE. If you want to play in the Digest Mode, you should input
the code GIL AND KI. Once this is done you will be transported to a level
select screen where you are offered the round of your choice.


MIDNIGHT RESISTANCE
===================
Stage Select - At the title screen, hold button C and press START. When you
begin playing, press START to pause. While paused, hit button A to advance
a level.


MIGHT & MAGIC
=============
Free Food - In your list of commands, select (Share and then Food). Do this
several times and your entire party's food supply will increase. You may
also go beyond the limit of 40 units with this trick.


MOONWALKER
==========
Stage Select - To select any stage but 6, hold UP, LEFT, and button A on
controller 2. Then push START on controller 1 and select a one player game.
After pushing START, you will see the words "Round 1." Press LEFT or RIGHT
to select the levels and press START.


M.U.S.H.A.
=========
Round Select - Reset the game four times, then hold DOWN and LEFT. Go to the
option mode and you will get a round select mode.


OUTRUN
======
New Difficulty Level - Press the C button 10 times before selecting the
options screen. When you do, you will see a new difficulty level called 
"Hyper", after you scroll past the level called "Pro."


QUAD CHALLENGE
==============
