PHELIOS
=======
Nine Times Continue - Get into the Chapter 1 intro screen and press buttons
C, A, B, A, C, A, B, A.


PIT FIGHTER
===========
Two Player Practice Mode - Start off the practice mode with one player and
have the second player join in after you have started fighting. All three
(the two players and the computer opponent) will have to fight it out to see
who is the last one standing.

Extra Continues - Play the character to Match 8, where you fight Mad Miles
for the second tim. Pause the game and plug in controller 2. Unpause the game
and then press START on the second controller. Withcontroller 2, select your
fighter and you will have three extra continues. Beat up your former fighter
and use your current one to take you through the remaining matches.


POWERBALL
=========
Play Four New Teams - In the first player league, pause the game. Press
B, B, C, B, B, C. You will hear a bell. At this time, push DOWN on the
controller and you will be able to select four more teams that are not
normally revealed.


PREDATOR 2
==========
Level Codes:  Level 2:  KILLERS
              Level 3:  CAMOFLAGE
              Level 4:  LOS ANGELES
              Level 5:  SUBTERROR
              Level 6:  TOTAL BODY


RBI 3
=====
Shutout / No Hitter - To strike out every batter, satnd on the mound opposite
the batter and throw to the outside of the plate. The batter will swing at 
every pitch and will always miss.


REVENGE OF SHINOBI
==================
Unlimited Knives - In the option screen, change the number of weapons to 00
and wait for ten seconds, not touching anything. The 00 will become an
infinity sign and you will never run out.


ROAD RASH
=========
Level Codes - These will give you the top bike and a large sum of money for
each level. The code for level 5 will give you the best bike money can buy,
but also over $60,000. Careful with the letters and numbers. 1 and 0 are
numbers, and I and O are letters.

      Level 1        Level 2        Level 3        Level 4        Level 5
   00000  07DJ1   00000  07O71   00000  07QF0   00000  083O0   00000  083S1
   12G9A  1786E   13IJJ  2N7SR   03JS3  37GL5   12NIK  473FC   12K38  5782A

Unlimited Money - This password will start you on the fourth level with over
7 million dollars. Now you can buy any bike before any race. Either crash
your bike, get caught by the cops or finish the race and you will be able to
see your cash and then buy yur bike!  34441  01MS0
                                      NV8UC  3QJ8R

Money Trick - Skip to the third level with $31 million: 010B0 01DB5
                                                        UQP06 37UN9


