SAGAIA
======
Unlimited Continues - At the title, press B, B, B, C, A, A, A, B, B, C, C, C.
THE Words "Free Play" will be at the bottom of the screen and when you lose
your last ship, you will have unlimited continues.

Stage Select - At the title, press C, A, C, B, C, A, B, A, B, C, A, C. The
words "Zone Select" will appear and you can now select one of the levels.


